videos.headline: Smith rips off 33-yard run
videos.description: Southern Miss RB Ito Smith breaks a tackle and burst up the field for a 33-yard gain.

videos.headline: Southern Miss QB Griggs dives for TD
videos.description: Kwadra Griggs has no where to throw the ball and takes it in himself, diving for the 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Blackman-Tate connection ties game up
videos.description: FSU's James Blackman finds Auden Tate for a 20-yard touchdown to knot the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: FSU's Tate makes tough catch
videos.description: James Blackman fires a pass  to Auden Tate and he makes the catch while being sandwiched between two defenders.

videos.headline: FSU takes the lead with Aker's TD
videos.description: James Blackman hits RB Cam Aker on a quick out route and he takes it in for a 14-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Blackman-Tate TD connection extends lead for FSU
videos.description: James Blackman finds Auden Tate for a 10-yard touchdown to widen the Seminoles' lead to 23-6 over Southern Miss.

videos.headline: Sanders coy about joining FSU coaching staff
videos.description: Pro Football Hall of Famer Deion Sanders responds to speculation that he is returning to his alma mater to be an assistant for new head coach Willie Taggart.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Deion coy about joining FSU coaching staff) 2017/12/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Southern Miss goes into bag of tricks to pick up first down
videos.description: Golden Eagles' P Zach Everett throws a pass to LB Allen Fails who turns up field for a 25-yard gain.

videos.headline: Patrick's TD opens the game wide open for FSU
videos.description: Florida State RB Jacques Patrick runs through a gauntlet of defenders for the 2-yard touchdown against Southern Mississippi.

videos.headline: Blackman connects with Tate on 3rd TD of the game
videos.description: Florida State's James Blackman throws it up to WR Auden Tate who makes a nice grab for the 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Florida State fan enjoying bowl win
videos.description: An FSU fan dances during a break during the Seminoles 42-13 win over Southern Miss.
